{"id":"d7cc49765e90ea651e1a96153556b2c9a2e7dd9d0db3913084df9d23f9f1647f","item_id":"dd41c144e5:0","text":"从版本 24 开始，RenderMan 包含一个全新的 diagnostics sub-system（诊断子系统），该系统从头重写，用于纳入 live（实时）、configurable statistics（可配置统计信息）。请参见 RenderMan 页面"}
{"id":"fcec91509759ad995c2cd14bcb26b2720993faf61c29d379b270d442d92290eb","item_id":"dd41c144e5:1","text":"此处"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"dd41c144e5:2","text":"。"}
{"id":"a903a293d9eb401fea8de4f582edb81f5048c81bf11eb92d8c814125758956ef","item_id":"dd41c144e5:3","text":"要继续使用 legacy statistics（旧版统计信息），请勾选"}
{"id":"e37d2dac77451a7401295fe23c8f179137984e6597bd2261ab9b59074004d296","item_id":"dd41c144e5:4","text":"Render Statistics（渲染统计）"}
{"id":"c95e76f2fa2886deaf939b9564dc3e80dc0e95bf1e747b7584574c041b8df39b","item_id":"dd41c144e5:5","text":"选项，位置在你的 RenderMan RIS ROP 的"}
{"id":"7e0d42307c38f463570d9e5953c99394b748424b29e8b8a47ee288d04074d351","item_id":"dd41c144e5:6","text":"Options | Statistics（选项 | 统计）"}
{"id":"e76128b80aaa71eb9d7b280cc1295b9308f71f724be77a340665444710bdb18c","item_id":"dd41c144e5:7","text":"Tab（选项卡）："}
{"id":"de37280f77fb930c2dbefe3b4d521ea5cf7a5109e77ddb63e0877ac9b24062e1","item_id":"dd41c144e5:8","text":"默认情况下，它使用 Disk File（磁盘文件）的路径和 base name（基本名称）。"}
{"id":"85f9bd962375c4f59ec8a794ed45fa7984e1a7c1191f1df72cd588ac552403ca","item_id":"dd41c144e5:9","text":"你可以用任何 Web browser（网页浏览器）查看输出的 XML file（XML 文件）。请参见"}
{"id":"817e36c5fad8df7c381b769f3d0dd4f52e7aa51ade629853d413e607263315b3","item_id":"dd41c144e5:10","text":"Legacy Diagnostics（旧版诊断）"}
{"id":"0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792","item_id":"dd41c144e5:11","text":"了解更多信息。"}
{"id":"50009ce1da4d15e1c4a04024df691eed5f0d598e2c4c67092f205366d0adf99e","item_id":"dd41c144e5:12","text":"File（文件）"}
{"id":"ae8bbec36a3f97d4ebedb296c4bd0a34ba55669e2318b5748c51a1671c17aa43","item_id":"dd41c144e5:13","text":"：生成 .stats 文件"}
{"id":"823c4301a039397f90a68f12ad613d3712c1d986b1ce3cb6105dc3b268bdaafa","item_id":"dd41c144e5:14","text":"XML File（XML 文件）"}
{"id":"2fedaa81f448b467e397c6a0dd363669a1dd6b5cfa60b39abcf41e16cb0666e7","item_id":"dd41c144e5:15","text":"：生成可在 browser（浏览器）中查看的 XML 文件"}
{"id":"454910739d52c7e6ac4eb31e68c4bce1d582caad167ad1003578d0a02ed990a2","item_id":"dd41c144e5:16","text":"IO Trace Filename（IO 跟踪文件名）"}
{"id":"e2da4890a4c3cec0391ebe48533e196c1682620c6d183825714ad7e01351b44c","item_id":"dd41c144e5:17","text":"：保存为 XML 的详细 input/output（输入/输出）报告"}
{"id":"45250097e5f0fa2ac0db6dcf2e548125715cb3c55795821d0764a3ab44fcdfa9","item_id":"dd41c144e5:18","text":"Stylesheet（样式表）"}
{"id":"3f0993caa1f43db3c580dc083ff6e5f12d4fba6b1c7e77241799125f3e6ffcfe","item_id":"dd41c144e5:19","text":"：用于格式化 XML 文件的 stylesheet（样式表）"}
{"id":"11677e295d52c58b3c1133daeebbc84e323c4f0648cd23014cff9e4054a24491","item_id":"dd41c144e5:20","text":"Shader Profile（着色器性能剖析）"}
{"id":"0a3e878543c31a23c014941466a27f36f056a5a1325f1a8b645eb973aa832acb","item_id":"dd41c144e5:21","text":"：用于 custom shader output（自定义着色器输出）的 profile（性能剖析）"}
{"id":"1cfdfe3611a46d1ae48ea7088fedf878187bca60570d4eb1bb0eb6ec89c9abe7","item_id":"dd41c144e5:22","text":"Displace Ratios（位移比率）"}
{"id":"c4dd82d2ba0510c28819793c841dd7ccc1aafc9da3492eedd873c0f9abdd737e","item_id":"dd41c144e5:23","text":"：当 displacement values（位移值）除以 max displacement（最大位移）后的结果落在此范围内时，抑制该报告"}
{"id":"5a6697416f8feb4141fb3f987c4cf3e2c998b4d380a78bc914221752f6782181","item_id":"dd41c144e5:24","text":"Maximum Displacement（最大位移）"}
{"id":"c2dc39f462e164742225aaa492a13d312a5e4493b77ed16b270e74a20f7c6df2","item_id":"dd41c144e5:25","text":"：停止前要打印的 displacement values（位移值）警告数量；0 表示报告所有值"}
{"id":"85c348b6078e908f5f1ce565c59c6c2d0358b483a56d16a43ce7b0c387eed480","item_id":"dd41c144e5:26","text":"Enable Texture Statistics（启用纹理统计）"}
{"id":"1a6bdbf5a6b0f5a40b0d279c12ffd23988e546e2dba2055dc60cb8e3ac125985","item_id":"dd41c144e5:27","text":"：允许对 texture usage（纹理使用情况）进行更细粒度的报告"}
{"id":"c2d5d52bca68f484edba64372b7267c98f54e854dd36889cb55bf980174c47df","item_id":"dd41c144e5:28","text":"Track Asset Objects（跟踪资产对象）"}
{"id":"1ddf557dd78dd0fb4cab11e44d86c3a8dd4a9bd5627d28ae152ed649287c9e46","item_id":"dd41c144e5:29","text":"：跟踪 scene entities（场景实体）"}
